Intended usage: COMMON

SPDX is an open standard. It is intended to be used to enable companies and organizations to share human-readable and machine-processable system package metadata to facilitate secure and compliant supply chain processes. An SPDX 3 JSON media type will be associated with a particular system package or set of packages and will contain information about it in the SPDX 3 JSON format.

